= Viewpoint activation =

Before using the Mode & States viewpoint, it needs to be activated.
In order to do so, you need to:

Open the Viewpoint Manager view by choosing Window / Show View / Other...

[[Image:showview.png]]

Type viewpoint in the search field and choose the Viewpoint Manager view

[[Image:showview2.png]]

The Viewpoint Manager view opens. Select a model element in order to synchronize the view with the status of a model.
By default, the viewpoint is "unreferenced"

[[Image:viewpointmanager.png]]

Right click on the "ms" viewpoint and select reference

[[Image:activation.png]]

The viewpoint is now "active" and can be used

[[Image:activated.png]]